		<pb n="1"/>
			<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Montreal</placeName> <date>Oct 29&#47;5609</date>&#45;</p>
			<p><addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
          <p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>&#45;</p>
          <p rend="indent(2)">My dear sir&#45;</p>
          <p rend="indent(3)">At the request of the Montreal Committee for<lb/> the relief of the Persecuted Persian Jews I beg to request<lb/> you to take <add>&#63;</add> for the <add>&#63;</add> of the republication<lb/> in any of the <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName> papers of the name of <persName>R Nissim ben<add>&#63;</add><lb/> Solomon</persName> an accredited messenger from our oppressed Persian brethren<lb/> in connection with a lecture delivered here by myself in their behalf.<lb/> The publication of his name he subsequently considers may prove<lb/> injurious to him&#44; and altho the committee &#40;<add>&#63;</add> enter into<lb/> his fears yet they bow in deference to them.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">Again requesting you to give the above your<lb/> immediate and best attention I am dear sir</p>
          <p rend="indent(11)">Truly yours</p>
          <p rend="indent(11)"><persName role="author">Abraham de Sola</persName></p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">The above&#44; dear Friend&#44; bears an official aspect. <persName>R Nissim</persName><lb/> in whom I take a great interest&#44; fears that the news may go back<lb/> to <placeName>Russia</placeName> that he has been telling naughty things of them&#44; I<lb/> <sic>dont</sic> fear any thing of the sort. Let me hear your opinion&#8212;<lb/> would you like a notice or <add>&#63;</add> of the article&#8212;I shall<lb/> answer your last as soon as I possibly can. I have been and<lb/> am yet too busy to do so. Till then <add>Hebrew</add></p>
          <p rend="indent(1)"><hi rend="underline">Dont give the above publicly till I write you again</hi>. <persName role="author">ADS</persName>.</p>
		<pb n="2"/>
			<p><addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
